<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-left:solid #4299E1 3.0pt;
padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 9.0pt;background:#EDF2F7'><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>project2/<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── <span class=SpellE>config.php</span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>              </span>← <span
class=SpellE>Konfigurasi</span> DB, auth, helper global<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── <span class=SpellE>setup.php</span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>               </span>← Install database <span
class=SpellE>pertama</span> kali<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── <span class=SpellE>login.php</span>, <span
class=SpellE>logout.php</span>, <span class=SpellE>register.php</span>, <span
class=SpellE>dashboard.php</span>, <span class=SpellE>search.php</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── <span class=SpellE>barang</span>/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>                 </span>← CRUD master <span
class=SpellE>barang</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'>├── supplier/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>               </span>← CRUD supplier<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── <span class=SpellE>pengguna</span>/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>               </span>← <span
class=SpellE>Manajemen</span> user<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── <span class=SpellE>referensi</span>/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>              </span>← Master data (<span
class=SpellE>kategori</span>, <span class=SpellE>satuan</span>, <span
class=SpellE>warna</span>, <span class=SpellE>merek</span>, <span class=SpellE>lokasi</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── <span class=SpellE>pemesanan</span>/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>              </span>← <span
class=SpellE>Pemesanan</span> <span class=SpellE>ke</span> supplier<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── <span class=SpellE>transaksi</span>/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>              </span>← Riwayat &amp; <span
class=SpellE>catat</span> <span class=SpellE>barang</span> <span class=SpellE>keluar</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── <span class=SpellE>laporan</span>/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>                </span>← <span
class=SpellE>Laporan</span> + <span class=SpellE>versi</span> <span
class=SpellE>cetak</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'>├── <span
class=SpellE>api</span>/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>                    </span>← Endpoint AJAX/JSON<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── auth/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>                   </span>← Session API<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>├── includes/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>               </span>← Layout, CSS, JS, schema, helper ROP<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>└── database/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>               </span>← File SQL <span
class=SpellE>awal</span> (project2.sql)<o:p></o:p></span></pre></div>

