<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><!-- ==================== BAGIAN 3 ==================== -->3.
Flow <span class=SpellE>Penggunaan</span> <span class=SpellE>Aplikasi</span>
(Alur <span class=SpellE>Kerja</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

</div>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.1
Flow Umum — Dari Login <span class=SpellE>sampai</span> Logout<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-left:solid #4299E1 3.0pt;
padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 9.0pt;background:#EDF2F7'><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>[Buka Browser]<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>     </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>[<span class=SpellE>index.php</span>] → redirect <span
class=SpellE>ke</span> <span class=SpellE>login.php</span> (<span class=SpellE>jika</span> <span
class=SpellE>belum</span> login)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>     </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>[<span class=SpellE>login.php</span>] → input email + password → <span
class=SpellE>verifikasi</span> <span class=SpellE>ke</span> <span class=SpellE>tabel</span> users<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>     </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>[<span class=SpellE>dashboard.php</span>] → <span
class=SpellE>ringkasan</span> <span class=SpellE>stok</span>, <span
class=SpellE>transaksi</span> <span class=SpellE>terbaru</span>, <span
class=SpellE>barang</span> <span class=SpellE>menipis</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>     </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>[Sidebar Navigation] → <span class=SpellE>pilih</span> <span
class=SpellE>modul</span> <span class=SpellE>sesuai</span> role<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>     </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>[Modul: Master / <span class=SpellE>Pemesanan</span> / <span
class=SpellE>Transaksi</span> / <span class=SpellE>Laporan</span>]<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>     </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>[<span class=SpellE>logout.php</span>] → hapus session → <span
class=SpellE>kembali</span> <span class=SpellE>ke</span> login<o:p></o:p></span></pre></div>

