<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.3
Flow Master Data (Owner/Admin)<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-left:solid #4299E1 3.0pt;
padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 9.0pt;background:#EDF2F7'><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>Setup <span class=SpellE>awal</span>:<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
class=SpellE>referensi</span>/ → <span class=SpellE>isi</span> <span
class=SpellE>Kategori</span>, <span class=SpellE>Satuan</span>, Warna, Merek, Lokasi<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>supplier<span
class=GramE>/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>→</span> <span
class=SpellE>tambah</span> data supplier (nama, <span class=SpellE>kontak</span>, <span
class=SpellE>alamat</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span style='color:
#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span class=SpellE>barang</span>/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>tambah</span> <span class=SpellE>barang</span> (nama, <span
class=SpellE>harga</span>, <span class=SpellE>stok</span> <span class=SpellE>awal</span>, <span
class=SpellE>kategori</span>, supplier)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
class=SpellE>pengguna</span>/<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>kelola</span> user (hapus user yang <span class=SpellE>tidak</span> <span
class=SpellE>perlu</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></pre></div>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.4
Flow Barang Masuk (Stok Naik) — UTAMA<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-left:solid #4299E1 3.0pt;
padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 9.0pt;background:#EDF2F7'><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>[Owner/Admin]<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
class=SpellE>pemesanan</span>/<span class=SpellE>form.php</span> → <span
class=SpellE>buat</span> <span class=SpellE>pesanan</span> <span class=SpellE>baru</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>pilih</span> <span class=SpellE>barang</span> (dropdown <span
class=SpellE>warna</span>: <span class=SpellE>merah</span>=<span class=SpellE>kritis</span>, <span
class=SpellE>kuning</span>=<span class=SpellE>menipis</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>isi</span> <span class=SpellE>jumlah</span> <span class=SpellE>pesanan</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ status <span
class=SpellE>awal</span>: &quot;<span class=SpellE>Diproses</span>&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
class=SpellE>pemesanan</span>/<span class=SpellE>index.php</span> → <span
class=SpellE>klik</span> &quot;Proses&quot; pada <span class=SpellE>pesanan</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ modal <span
class=SpellE>ubah</span> status<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>pilih</span> &quot;<span class=SpellE>Diterima</span>&quot; + <span
class=SpellE>tanggal</span> <span class=SpellE>diterima</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
class=SpellE>pemesanan</span>/<span class=SpellE>update_status.php</span> (POST, backend)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>stok_saat_ini</span> += <span class=SpellE>jumlah_pesan</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ insert <span
class=SpellE>transaksi</span> <span class=SpellE>jenis</span>='<span
class=SpellE>masuk</span>'<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>hitung</span> <span class=SpellE>ulang</span> ROP (includes/<span
class=SpellE>rop.php</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
class=SpellE>transaksi</span>/<span class=SpellE>masuk.php</span> → <span
class=SpellE>lihat</span> <span class=SpellE>riwayat</span> <span class=SpellE>barang</span> <span
class=SpellE>masuk</span> (READ ONLY)<o:p></o:p></span></pre></div>

<div style='border:none;border-left:solid #E53E3E 3.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 11.0pt;
margin-top:9.0pt;margin-bottom:9.0pt'>

<p class=MsoNormal style='background:#FFF5F5'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#1A202C'>Tab <strong><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Barang
Masuk</span></strong> TIDAK punya form input. <span class=SpellE>Semua</span> <span
class=SpellE>barang</span> <span class=SpellE>masuk</span> <span class=SpellE>lewat</span>
<span class=SpellE>alur</span> <span class=SpellE>Pemesanan</span> → <span
class=SpellE>Diterima</span>. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

</div>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.5
Flow Barang <span class=SpellE>Keluar</span> (Stok Turun)<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-left:solid #4299E1 3.0pt;
padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 9.0pt;background:#EDF2F7'><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>[Owner / Admin / <span class=SpellE>Karyawan</span>]<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
class=SpellE>transaksi</span>/<span class=SpellE>index.php</span> → <span
class=SpellE>klik</span> <span class=SpellE>tombol</span> <span class=SpellE>merah</span> &quot;Barang <span
class=SpellE>Keluar</span>&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
class=SpellE>transaksi</span>/<span class=SpellE>catat_keluar.php</span> → form <span
class=SpellE>catat</span> <span class=SpellE>keluar</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>pilih</span> <span class=SpellE>barang</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>isi</span> <span class=SpellE>jumlah</span> (max = <span
class=SpellE>stok</span> <span class=SpellE>saat</span> <span class=SpellE>ini</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ preview <span
class=SpellE>stok</span> &amp; <span class=SpellE>estimasi</span> ROP (AJAX <span
class=SpellE>ke</span> <span class=SpellE>api</span>/<span class=SpellE>hitung_rop.php</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
class=SpellE>transaksi</span>/<span class=SpellE>proses_keluar.php</span> (POST, backend)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>validasi</span> <span class=SpellE>stok</span> <span class=SpellE>cukup</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>stok_saat_ini</span> -= <span class=SpellE>jumlah</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ insert <span
class=SpellE>transaksi</span> <span class=SpellE>jenis</span>='<span
class=SpellE>keluar</span>'<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span style='color:
#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ <span class=SpellE>hitung</span> <span
class=SpellE>ulang</span> ROP<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>→ warning <span
class=SpellE>jika</span> <span class=SpellE>stok</span> <span class=SpellE>menipis</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>↓<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
class=SpellE>transaksi</span>/<span class=SpellE>keluar.php</span> → <span
class=SpellE>lihat</span> <span class=SpellE>riwayat</span> <span class=SpellE>barang</span> <span
class=SpellE>keluar</span> (READ ONLY)<o:p></o:p></span></pre></div>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.6
Flow <span class=SpellE>Laporan</span><o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-left:solid #4299E1 3.0pt;
padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 9.0pt;background:#EDF2F7'><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre><span
class=SpellE><span style='color:#1A202C'>laporan</span></span><span
style='color:#1A202C'>/<span class=SpellE>index.php</span> → redirect <span
class=SpellE>ke</span> <span class=SpellE>laporan</span>/<span class=SpellE>barang_tersedia.php</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>├── <span
class=SpellE><span class=GramE>barang_tersedia.php</span></span><span
class=GramE><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>→</span> <span
class=SpellE>stok</span> + status (Aman/<span class=SpellE>Menipis</span>/<span
class=SpellE>Kritis</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span style='color:
#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>├── <span class=SpellE>stok.php</span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>             </span>→ detail <span
class=SpellE>stok</span> per <span class=SpellE>barang</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>├── <span
class=SpellE>barang_masuk.php</span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>     </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>laporan</span> <span class=SpellE>masuk</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>├── <span
class=SpellE>barang_keluar.php</span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>laporan</span> <span class=SpellE>keluar</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>├── <span
class=SpellE>pemasok.php</span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>          </span>→ data supplier<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>└── <span
class=SpellE>cetak</span>/*.<span class=SpellE>php</span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>          </span>→ <span
class=SpellE>versi</span> print-friendly<o:p></o:p></span></pre></div>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.7
Diagram Alur Stok (<span class=SpellE>Ringkas</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-left:solid #4299E1 3.0pt;
padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 9.0pt;background:#EDF2F7'><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>                    </span>┌─────────────────┐<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>                    </span><span
class=GramE>│<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Master</span> <span
class=GramE>Barang<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>│</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>                    </span><span
class=GramE>│<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>(</span><span
class=SpellE>stok_saat_<span class=GramE>ini</span></span><span class=GramE>)│</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
