<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4.3
Pola Database Transaction (PENTING)<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:#1A202C'>File
proses <span class=SpellE>stok</span> (</span><span class=SpellE><code><span
style='font-size:9.5pt;color:#1A202C'>update_status.php</span></code></span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:#1A202C'>, </span><span
class=SpellE><code><span style='font-size:9.5pt;color:#1A202C'>proses_keluar.php</span></code></span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:#1A202C'>) <span
class=SpellE>memakai</span> <span class=SpellE>pola</span> <span class=SpellE>aman</span>:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-left:solid #4299E1 3.0pt;
padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 9.0pt;background:#EDF2F7'><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>$<span class=SpellE>pdo</span>-&gt;<span class=SpellE><span
class=GramE>beginTransaction</span></span><span class=GramE>(</span>);<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>$<span class=SpellE>stmt</span> = $<span class=SpellE>pdo</span>-&gt;<span
class=GramE>prepare(</span>'SELECT ... FROM <span class=SpellE>barang</span> WHERE id <span
class=GramE>= ?</span> FOR UPDATE');<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>// FOR UPDATE = <span class=SpellE>kunci</span> baris agar 2 user <span
class=SpellE>tidak</span> update <span class=SpellE>stok</span> <span
class=SpellE>bersamaan</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>// ... update <span class=SpellE>stok</span> + insert <span
class=SpellE>transaksi</span> ...<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre><span
style='color:#1A202C'>$<span class=SpellE>pdo</span>-&gt;<span class=GramE>commit();<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span></span>// <span
class=SpellE>sukses</span> → <span class=SpellE>simpan</span> <span
class=SpellE>semua</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'>// <span
class=SpellE>atau</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre><span style='color:#1A202C'>$<span
class=SpellE>pdo</span>-&gt;<span class=SpellE><span class=GramE>rollBack</span></span><span
class=GramE>(</span>); // <span class=SpellE>gagal</span> → <span class=SpellE>batalkan</span> <span
class=SpellE>semua</span>, <span class=SpellE>stok</span> <span class=SpellE>tidak</span> <span
class=SpellE>berubah</span> <span class=SpellE>sebagian</span><o:p></o:p></span></pre></div>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4.4
<span class=SpellE>Keamanan</span> Dasar (PENTING)<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul style='margin-top:0cm' type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='color:#1A202C;margin-top:2.25pt;margin-bottom:2.25pt;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span class=GramE><code><span
     style='font-size:9.5pt'>h(</span></code></span><code><span
     style='font-size:9.5pt'>)</span></code><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
     — escape HTML output → <span class=SpellE>cegah</span> XSS<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='color:#1A202C;margin-top:2.25pt;margin-bottom:2.25pt;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span class=SpellE><code><span
     style='font-size:9.5pt'>password_<span class=GramE>hash</span></span></code></span><span
     class=GramE><code><span style='font-size:9.5pt'>(</span></code></span><code><span
     style='font-size:9.5pt'>)</span></code><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
     / </span><span class=SpellE><code><span style='font-size:9.5pt'>password_<span
     class=GramE>verify</span></span></code></span><span class=GramE><code><span
     style='font-size:9.5pt'>(</span></code></span><code><span
     style='font-size:9.5pt'>)</span></code><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
     — password <span class=SpellE>tidak</span> <span class=SpellE>disimpan</span>
     plain text<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='color:#1A202C;margin-top:2.25pt;margin-bottom:2.25pt;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='font-size:
     11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>PDO
     Prepared Statement (</span><code><span style='font-size:9.5pt'>?</span></code><span
     style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>) — <span class=SpellE>cegah</span> SQL Injection<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='color:#1A202C;margin-top:2.25pt;margin-bottom:2.25pt;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='font-size:
     11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Cek
     </span><code><span style='font-size:9.5pt'>$_SERVER['REQUEST_METHOD'] ===
     'POST'</span></code><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> di file proses<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4.5
Bug Pagination (<span class=SpellE>sudah</span> <span class=SpellE>diperbaiki</span>
— <span class=SpellE>waspadai</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:#1A202C'>COUNT
query <span class=SpellE>harus</span> <span class=SpellE>pakai</span> JOIN yang
<span class=SpellE>sama</span> <span class=SpellE>dengan</span> SELECT. Jika <span
class=SpellE>tidak</span>, <span class=SpellE>halaman</span> 2 <span
class=SpellE>bisa</span> <span class=SpellE>kosong</span> <span class=SpellE>padahal</span>
<span class=SpellE>ada</span> data. <span class=SpellE>Berlaku</span> di: <span
class=SpellE>transaksi</span>/, <span class=SpellE>laporan</span>/<span
class=SpellE>barang_tersedia.php</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid #BEE3F8 1.0pt;
mso-border-bottom-alt:solid #BEE3F8 .75pt;padding:0cm 0cm 3.0pt 0cm'>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><!-- ==================== BAGIAN 5 ==================== -->5.
Cara <span class=SpellE>Rumus</span> ROP <span class=SpellE>Diterapkan</span> <span
class=SpellE>ke</span> Coding<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

</div>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>5.1
Apa <span class=SpellE>itu</span> ROP?<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p><strong><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
color:#1A202C'>ROP (Reorder Point)</span></strong><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:#1A202C'> = <span class=SpellE>titik</span>
<span class=SpellE>stok</span> minimum <span class=SpellE>untuk</span> <span
class=SpellE>memesan</span> <span class=SpellE>ulang</span> <span class=SpellE>barang</span>.<br>
<strong><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Safety Stock</span></strong>
= <span class=SpellE>cadangan</span> <span class=SpellE>stok</span> <span
class=SpellE>untuk</span> <span class=SpellE>antisipasi</span> <span
class=SpellE>permintaan</span>/<span class=SpellE>lebih</span> lama <span
class=SpellE>dari</span> <span class=SpellE>biasanya</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>5.2
<span class=SpellE>Rumus</span> <span class=SpellE>Matematika</span><o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<div style='border:solid #D6BCFA 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #D6BCFA .75pt;
padding:9.0pt 9.0pt 9.0pt 9.0pt;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt'>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center;background:#FAF5FF'><strong><span
style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#1A202C'>Metode <span class=SpellE>lengkap</span></span></strong><span
style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#1A202C'> (<span class=SpellE>jika</span> <span class=SpellE>ada</span>
data <span class=SpellE>permintaan</span> &amp; lead time):<br>
<br>
Safety Stock = (Demand Max × Lead Time Max) − (Demand Avg × Lead Time Avg)<br>
<br>
ROP = (Demand Avg × Lead Time Avg) + Safety Stock <o:p></o:p></span></p>

</div>

<div style='border:solid #D6BCFA 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #D6BCFA .75pt;
padding:9.0pt 9.0pt 9.0pt 9.0pt;margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt'>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center;background:#FAF5FF'><strong><span
style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#1A202C'>Metode fallback</span></strong><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#1A202C'> (<span class=SpellE>jika</span>
<span class=SpellE>belum</span> <span class=SpellE>ada</span> <span
class=SpellE>riwayat</span> <span class=SpellE>transaksi</span> <span
class=SpellE>keluar</span>):<br>
<br>
Safety Stock = <span class=GramE>max(</span>3, <span class=SpellE>stok</span> ×
20%)<br>
ROP = <span class=GramE>max(</span>10, <span class=SpellE>stok</span> × 40%) <o:p></o:p></span></p>

</div>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>5.3
<span class=SpellE>Variabel</span> <span class=SpellE>dalam</span> Database (<span
class=SpellE>tabel</span> <span class=SpellE>barang</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

