<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>5.6
<span class=SpellE>Contoh</span> <span class=SpellE>Perhitungan</span> <span
class=SpellE>Nyata</span><o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<div style='border:none;border-left:solid #3182CE 3.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 11.0pt;
margin-top:9.0pt;margin-bottom:9.0pt'>

<p class=MsoNormal style='background:#EBF8FF'><span class=SpellE><strong><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
"Times New Roman";color:#1A202C'>Contoh</span></strong></span><strong><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
"Times New Roman";color:#1A202C'>:</span></strong><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#1A202C'> Barang &quot;<span class=SpellE>Sabun</span> <span
class=SpellE>Cair</span>&quot; — 30 <span class=SpellE>hari</span> <span
class=SpellE>terakhir</span> <span class=SpellE>ada</span> 10 <span
class=SpellE>hari</span> <span class=SpellE>transaksi</span> <span
class=SpellE>keluar</span>.<br>
Total <span class=SpellE>keluar</span> per <span class=SpellE>hari</span>: [5,
8, 3, 10, 7, 4, 6, 9, 2, 5] unit<br>
<br>
<span class=SpellE>demand_avg</span> = (5+8+3+10+7+4+6+9+2+5) / 10 = <strong><span
style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>5.9 unit/<span class=SpellE>hari</span></span></strong><br>
<span class=SpellE>demand_max</span> = <strong><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>10
unit/<span class=SpellE>hari</span></span></strong><br>
<span class=SpellE>delivery_avg</span> = 3 <span class=SpellE>hari</span>, <span
class=SpellE>delivery_max</span> = 5 <span class=SpellE>hari</span><br>
<br>
Safety Stock = (10 × 5) − (5.9 × 3) = 50 − 17.7 = <strong><span
style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>32 unit</span></strong><br>
ROP = (5.9 × 3) + 32 = 17.7 + 32 = <strong><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>50
unit</span></strong><br>
<br>
Jika <span class=SpellE>stok_saat_ini</span> = 45 → status = <span
class=SpellE><strong><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Menipis</span></strong></span>
(45 ≤ 50)<br>
Jika <span class=SpellE>stok_saat_ini</span> = 10 → status = <span
class=SpellE><strong><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Kritis</span></strong></span>
(10/50 = 20% &lt; 30%) <o:p></o:p></span></p>

</div>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid #BEE3F8 1.0pt;
mso-border-bottom-alt:solid #BEE3F8 .75pt;padding:0cm 0cm 3.0pt 0cm'>

