     11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
     — <span class=SpellE>buat</span> folder/<span class=SpellE>modul</span>/<span
     class=SpellE>index.php</span> <span class=SpellE>dengan</span> <span
     class=SpellE><span class=GramE>requireOwner</span></span><span
     class=GramE>(</span>) <span class=SpellE>atau</span> <span class=SpellE><span
     class=GramE>requireStaff</span></span><span class=GramE>(</span>)<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='color:#1A202C;margin-top:2.25pt;margin-bottom:2.25pt;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;background:#EBF8FF'><strong><span
     style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Form</span></strong><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
     — <span class=SpellE>modul</span>/<span class=SpellE>form.php</span>
     handle GET (<span class=SpellE>tampil</span>) + POST (<span class=SpellE>simpan</span>)
     <span class=SpellE>dalam</span> 1 file<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='color:#1A202C;margin-top:2.25pt;margin-bottom:2.25pt;
